headline: Jabil Board Shakeup Puts Governance And Growth Priorities In Focus
summary: Jabil (NYSE:JBL) has announced significant changes to its Board of Directors, including the appointment of a new Chairman. Two new directors with industry experience are joining the board as part of this leadership reshuffle. Two existing board members have offered their resignations after unsuccessful re election efforts by shareholders. For investors watching NYSE:JBL, these boardroom moves come at a time when the stock is trading at $236.06 and has delivered a 44.5% return over the past...

headline: SANM Rises 26.4% in the Past 6 Months: Should You Buy the Stock?
summary: SANM is up 26.4% in six months as IMS revenue surges, cash flow strengthens and valuation stays below peers - does the rally still have room?
